    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and optimized Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M-lock limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry performs as intended. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience.",
