      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained executive sedan that perfectly bridges the gap between luxury and daily utility. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic charcoal that retains a deep, brilliant shine. While the body is straight and free of major dents, a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium leather and wood accents. The upholstery is in excellent shape with no tears or stains, though there is some light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every feature, from the heated seats and navigation system to the premium 12-speaker audio setup, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, this car stands out; it has a comprehensive service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The turbocharged engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable. We recently fitted a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires and replaced the brake pads, ensuring this vehicle is turn-key ready for its next owner. This is a solid, honest car that has been treated with respect since day one.",
